description: Retrieves information about the specified access log subscription.

parameters.name: accessLogSubscriptionIdentifier
parameters.description: The ID or ARN of the access log subscription.

nested_items.name: arn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the access log subscription.

nested_items.name: createdAt
nested_items.description: The date and time that the access log subscription was created, in ISO-8601 format.

nested_items.name: destinationArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the access log destination.

nested_items.name: id
nested_items.description: The ID of the access log subscription.

nested_items.name: lastUpdatedAt
nested_items.description: The date and time that the access log subscription was last updated, in ISO-8601 format.

nested_items.name: resourceArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the service network or service.

nested_items.name: resourceId
nested_items.description: The ID of the service network or service.

nested_items.name: serviceNetworkLogType
nested_items.description: The log type for the service network.
